  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Action on HIV, Nutrition and Food Security in the Copperbelt of Zambia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project contributes to poverty reduction and improved nutritional status among poor and vulnerable HIV and AIDS affected and infected smallholder farmers in Kalulushi and Mufulira districts of Copperbelt Province in Zambia. It aims to improve availability and access to diverse food and income sources for up to 1,500 smallholder farmers and their families and to combat the HIV pandemic by building local capacity in targeted communities to impart leadership and provide care for the beneficiaries.</narrative>
  </description>
